trans-unit.source: Provides a standard set of component-related commands, which have predefined key input gestures and <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedUICommand.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder et standard sett med komponent-relaterte kommandoer, som har forhåndsdefinerte key inndata bevegelser og <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedUICommand.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName> egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: The commands in the ComponentCommands class and commands in the other command library classes, such as <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.NavigationCommands>, are intended to represent a set of common commands that application programmers encounter frequently.
trans-unit.target: Kommandoer i klassen ComponentCommands og kommandoer i en annen kommando biblioteket klasser som <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands>og <xref:System.Windows.Input.NavigationCommands>, er ment å representere et sett med vanlige kommandoer som programmet programmerere oppstår ofte.</xref:System.Windows.Input.NavigationCommands> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands>

trans-unit.source: The commands only represent the instance of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> and not the implementation logic for the command.
trans-unit.target: Kommandoene representerer bare forekomsten av den <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>og ikke implementering logikken for kommandoen.</xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>

trans-unit.source: The implementation logic is bound to the command via a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Implementering logikken er bundet til kommandoen via en <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> command is executed on a control (the command target), the logic that performs the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> command may not be provided by the command target, so the application writer is responsible for writing the logic that determines how the command target handles the command.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis den <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A>kommando er utført på en kontroll (kommandoen målet), logikken som utfører den <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A>kommandoen kan ikke være angitt av kommandoen for mål, så programmet skriveren er ansvarlig for å skrive logikken som bestemmer hvordan kommandoen målet håndterer kommandoen.</xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A>

trans-unit.source: Many controls do provide implementation logic, though, for many of the commands in the command library.
trans-unit.target: Mange kontroller gir implementering logic imidlertid for mange kommandoer i kommandoen-biblioteket.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> class provides logic for the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A> command, and <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A> command.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox>klassen gir logikken for den <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A>kommandoen, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A>kommandoen, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A>kommandoen, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A>kommandoen, og <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A>kommandoen.</xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox>

trans-unit.source: See the class documentation for particular control classes for more information.
trans-unit.target: Dokumentasjonen klasse for bestemt kontroll klasser for mer informasjon.

trans-unit.source: For more information on commands and commanding, see [Commanding Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om kommandoer og tiltrekker seg, se [tiltrekker seg oversikt over](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
